---
config:
  theme: dark
  themeVariables:
    primaryColor: "#1e1e1e"
    primaryBorderColor: "#333333"
    background: "#1e1e1e"
    mainBkg: "#2d2d2d"
    secondBkg: "#3d3d3d"
    textColor: "#e0e0e0"
    borderColor: "#555555"
---
flowchart TD
    Start([📄 Input: Text<br/>max_length,style,focus]) --> Analyze["<b>1. Analyze</b><br/>─────<br/>Deterministic text analysis<br/>Heuristic chunk sizing:<br/>≤2K → whole / 2-10K → 800ch<br/>≥10K → 1500ch chunks"]
    
    Analyze --> chunk_state["State:<br/>text_type, complexity<br/>chunk_size_recommendation"]
    
    chunk_state --> Chunk["<b>2. Chunk</b><br/>─────<br/>Semantic text chunking<br/>Respects cost/size targets<br/>Max 10 chunks"]
    
    Chunk --> chunk_out["State:<br/>chunks[] (semantic boundaries)"]
    
    chunk_out --> Summarize["<b>3. Summarize</b><br/>─────<br/>Sequential LLM calls per chunk<br/>Fallback: 500-char extraction<br/>Handles extraction failures"]
    
    Summarize --> sum_state["State:<br/>chunk_summaries[]<br/>fallback_count"]
    
    sum_state --> Synthesize["<b>4. Synthesize</b><br/>─────<br/>Combine chunk summaries<br/>Inject: focus area if provided<br/>Extract 3-5 key_points"]
    
    Synthesize --> syn_state["State:<br/>synthesis (narrative)<br/>key_points[]"]
    
    syn_state --> Evaluate["<b>5. Evaluate (Quality Gate)</b><br/>─────<br/>Score 3 dimensions:<br/>• Faithfulness (claims grounded)<br/>• Completeness (key points covered)<br/>• Coherence (structure/readability)"]
    
    Evaluate --> hallucination["Hallucination Penalty:<br/>─────<br/>Unsupported claims detected<br/>Score capped → max 0.3<br/>-0.05 per unsupported claim<br/>Returns: weakest_criterion"]
    
    hallucination --> eval_state["State:<br/>quality_score (0-1)<br/>score_history[]<br/>feedback for refinement"]
    
    eval_state --> Decision{"<b>Refine Loop?</b><br/>─────<br/>IF score < threshold<br/>AND rounds < max_loops<br/>AND NOT plateau<br/>plateau = Δscore < 0.02"}
    
    Decision -->|Yes| Refine["<b>6. Refine</b><br/>─────<br/>Target weakest criterion<br/>Provide source excerpts<br/>(start/middle/end sampling)<br/>Ground claims<br/>refinement_rounds++"]
    
    Decision -->|No| Format["<b>7. Format</b><br/>─────<br/>Apply style: paragraph|bullets|tldr<br/>Truncate to max_length<br/>Calculate word_count<br/>Set truncated flag"]
    
    Refine --> refine_back["Updated synthesis<br/>Loop back"]
    
    refine_back -->|Continue| Evaluate
    
    Format --> out_state["State:<br/>final_summary<br/>key_points[]<br/>word_count, truncated"]
    
    out_state --> Output["📊 Output:<br/>─────<br/>summary, key_points<br/>quality_score<br/>refinement_rounds<br/>word_count, truncated"]
    
    Output --> End([✅ Complete])
    
    style Start fill:#2d5016,stroke:#5cb85c,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px
    style End fill:#2d5016,stroke:#5cb85c,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px
    style Decision fill:#5a3d1a,stroke:#ffa500,color:#fff,stroke-width:3px
    style hallucination fill:#3a2020,stroke:#ff6b6b,color:#ffcccc
    style refine_back fill:#3a3a1e,stroke:#f9a825,color:#e0e0e0
    style Evaluate fill:#3d2d1a,stroke:#ff6b6b,color:#ff9999
    style Refine fill:#3d2d1a,stroke:#ff6b6b,color:#ff9999
    style Synthesize fill:#2d3d1a,stroke:#a6e3a1,color:#e0e0e0
